-\frac{1}{2}x^2 + 2x + 5 = 0
x^2-4x-10=0
x^2-2\cdot x\cdot2+2^2-2^2-10=0
x^2-2\cdot x\cdot2+2^2=4+10
(x-2)^2=14
x-2=\pm \sqrt{14}
x=2\pm \sqrt{14}
